org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.parser.v2.geometries

Class PolygonMemberTypeBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.parser.v2.geometries.PolygonMemberTypeBinding
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PolygonMemberTypeBinding

    public class PolygonMemberTypeBinding
extends Object
    It parses a gml:polygonMemberType object. Example: 

     
 <polygonMember>
 <Polygon gid="_877789">
 <outerBoundaryIs>
 <LinearRing>
 <coordinates>0.0,0.0 100.0,0.0 50.0,100.0 0.0,0.0</coordinates>
 </LinearRing>
 </outerBoundaryIs>
 </Polygon>
 </polygonMember>
